	<Title>
		Rheumatoid arthritis: Can it affect the eyes?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Although rheumatoid arthritis is primarily a joint disease, it occasionally affects the eyes.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Can rheumatoid arthritis affect the eyes?
	</Question>
